          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".HIGH-PURITY FUSED QUARTZ PLATES, SIO2, WITH 1 MM",
                " THICKNESS, WERE USED AS OXYGEN AND SILICON SAMPLES.",
                " THE SIO2 PLATES WERE WRAPPED WITH AL FOILS TO PREVENT",
                " 14-C CONTAMINATION OF TARGETS FROM AIR. HIGH-PURITY",
                " SILICON IN THE FORM OF THIN PLATES AND FLAKES WERE",
                " ALSO USED AS SILICON SAMPLES. THE IRRADIATION TIMES",
                " WERE TYPICALLY 2 - 3 HR."
              ]
            }
          ],
